    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. The engine is currently non-operational and requires a complete diagnostic and likely a rebuild, while the transmission shows signs of significant slipping. Externally, the body has several large dents, noticeable rust spots along the wheel wells, and the paint is heavily faded. The interior has seen better days, with torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. It will need to be towed from its current location.",
